title: Champs Elysees Executive Apartment
body:
QR Code Link to This Post


Champs Elysees Executive Apartment offers accommodations in Paris. The apartment is 2625 feet from Arc de Triomphe. Free WiFi is offered throughout the property.

An oven, a microwave and a toaster can be found in the kitchenette and there is a private bathroom with slippers and free toiletries. Towels and bed linen are provided in this apartment.
